This directory (third_party/xcursor-mini) is a vendored, X11-free subset of
libXcursor's .xcursor file loader, modified for static linking into drm-cxx.

Upstream:  libXcursor 1.2.3  (src/file.c)
Source:    https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/xorg/lib/libxcursor
License:   HPND-sell-variant (SPDX-License-Identifier)

